## Data Pipeline Flow

```
TheRacingAPI → Z1-Z8 scripts → race_data_YYYY_MM_DD.db (daily SQLite)
    → 01-08a feature engineering scripts → model_training_data table
    → predict_v2.py → predictions written to .db
    → push_to_supabase.py → Supabase race_entries table
    → Frontend reads from Supabase
```

## Supabase Tables (key ones)

**Column names for filtering/deleting:**
- `races` uses `date` column (not `race_date`) — e.g. `?date=eq.2026-03-19`
- `race_entries` has NO date column — delete by `race_id` (get race_ids from `races` first)

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `races` | Race metadata (course, time, class, distance, going) — date column is `date` |
| `race_entries` | Per-horse data including ML predictions (`rf_proba`, `xgboost_proba`, `benter_proba`, `ensemble_proba`), `opening_odds` (protected by trigger), `current_odds` (updated live) |
| `race_results` | Race result metadata |
| `race_runners` | Per-horse finishing positions |
| `dynamic_signal_combos` | Profitable signal patterns discovered by scanner |
| `bets` | User's manual bets (placed via frontend) |
| `user_bankroll` | User's bankroll balance |
| `auto_bet_ledger` | System auto-bets (DO NOT use for user-facing stats) |
| `ml_model_race_results` | Model prediction tracking |
| `horse_market_movement` | Legacy odds movement data (superseded by race_entries.opening_odds/current_odds) |

